data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Motivated Sellers, Bring ALL offers! Welcome to the epitome of modern living in the heart of the brand-new, amenity-rich master-planned community of North River Ranch. This newer residence, situated on an oversized pie-shaped lot, invites you to experience contemporary luxury with a blend of stylish upgrades.  Step inside to discover a home adorned with new fixtures throughout, highlighted by fresh paint that effortlessly adds a touch of sophistication. An eye-catching new accent wall sets the stage for chic and vibrant interiors. The kitchen, featuring newer appliances, is a culinary haven, complemented by a newly finished laundry room that adds both convenience and style. Venture outdoors to a fenced-in yard, providing privacy and security, and relish in the scenic beauty from your newly paved lanai overlooking a peaceful water view. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends and family, this outdoor space is a perfect retreat. Enjoy miles of greenways and trails, take advantage of the three amenity campuses, utilize the bike share, and stay active with multiple Avid Fit stations. Anticipate even more excitement with the upcoming brand-new Amenity campus, Camp Creek – an eagerly awaited addition to this thriving community. This residence in North River Ranch is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule a viewing today! *Some photos have been virtually staged to better showcase the true potential of rooms and spaces in the home.
